## 6. ARCHITECTURE & DATA FLOW

### Core copy-trading flow
```
[Tracked Wallets on Polymarket]
       │
       ├──→ WalletMonitor (polls Data API every 5s)
       │         │
       │         ▼
       │    parseTradeData() → DetectedTrade
       │         │
       └──→ DomeWebSocketMonitor (real-time via Dome SDK)
                 │
                 ▼
          handleOrderEvent() → DetectedTrade
                 │
                 ▼
         CopyTrader.handleDetectedTrade()
                 │
                 ├── Deduplication (txHash + compound key)
                 ├── In-flight guard
                 ├── Wallet config validation
                 ├── Side filter
                 ├── Price limits check
                 ├── No-repeat check
                 ├── Value filter
                 ├── Rate limit check
                 ├── Stop-loss check
                 ├── Trade sizing (fixed/proportional/global)
                 ├── Safety cap (2× configured size)
                 ├── Min order size check
                 ├── SELL: verify share ownership
                 │
                 ▼
         TradeExecutor.executeTrade()
                 │
                 ├── tokenId required
                 ├── Slippage adjustment
                 ├── PolymarketClobClient.createAndPostOrder()
                 │       │
                 │       ├── Derive L2 API key from wallet
                 │       ├── Create CLOB client with sig type + funder
                 │       └── POST order to CLOB
                 │
                 ▼
         Storage.addExecutedPosition()
         PerformanceTracker.recordTrade()
```

### Discovery Engine flow
```
[Polygon Chain]                    [Polymarket API]
      │                                  │
      ▼                                  ▼
 ChainListener                     ApiPoller
 (OrderFilled events               (REST polling
  via Alchemy WS)                   every 30s)
      │                                  │
      └──────────┬───────────────────────┘
                 │
                 ▼
          TradeIngestion
          (batch dedup + flush every 2s)
                 │
                 ▼
          DiscoveryManager
                 │
                 ├── WalletScorer (scoring algorithm)
                 ├── SignalEngine (anomaly detection)
                 ├── MarketClassifier
                 ├── PositionTracker
                 └── StatsStore (SQLite persistence)
                 │
                 ▼
          [Discovery Dashboard UI]
          (surface wallets for tracking)
```

### Two runtime modes
1. **`app`** (default): Express server + CopyTrader + monitoring
2. **`discovery-worker`**: Standalone discovery process (set `APP_RUNTIME=discovery-worker`)
3. `start.cjs` runs BOTH in parallel during development

