## 11. POLYMARKET AUTH (CRITICAL)

### Signature types
| Type | Name | When |
|------|------|------|
| 0 | EOA | Pure EOA with NO proxy (rare) |
| 1 | POLY_PROXY | Magic Link / email signup |
| **2** | **POLY_GNOSIS_SAFE** | **Browser wallet (MetaMask/Rabby) WITH proxy** |

### This project's setup
- **EOA**: `0x2D43e332aF357CAb0fa1b2692E1e0Fdb0B733010`
- **Proxy**: `0xD56276b120ad094ba9F429386427F2492233B6d1`
- **Signature type**: 2 (POLY_GNOSIS_SAFE)
- Funds live in the PROXY wallet, not the EOA

### CLOB client initialization (clobClient.ts)
1. Derive API key with ONLY the signer (no signatureType/funder)
2. Create full client WITH signatureType and funder address
3. Builder API creds prevent Cloudflare blocks on cloud servers

### Common errors
| Error | Cause | Fix |
|-------|-------|-----|
| "invalid signature" | Wrong signatureType | Use type 2 |
| "not enough balance" | Looking at EOA not proxy | Set POLYMARKET_FUNDER_ADDRESS to proxy |

