## 13. FRONTEND RULES

### Win95 UI
- All UI is Windows 95 themed (no modern frameworks)
- Custom dialog system in `public/js/app.js`:
  - `await win95Dialog.alert(message, title?)`
  - `await win95Dialog.success(message, title?)`
  - `await win95Dialog.error(message, title?)`
  - `await win95Dialog.confirm(message, title?)` → `true` | `false`
  - `await win95Dialog.prompt(message, defaultValue?, title?)` → `string` | `null`
- **NEVER** use native `alert()`, `confirm()`, `prompt()` — use `win95Dialog` instead
- All dialog calls are async — use `await`

### API client
- `public/js/api.js` wraps `fetch` with auth header from `sessionStorage.getItem('api_token')`
- Base path: `/api`

