## 14. SCHEDULING / INTERVALS

| Component | Interval | Purpose |
|-----------|----------|---------|
| WalletMonitor | 5s (configurable) | Poll for tracked wallet trades |
| DiscoveryManager | 5 min | Aggregate stats |
| Discovery ApiPoller | 30s | Poll Polymarket for trades |
| Discovery market refresh | 15 min | Refresh market metadata |
| ChainListener ping | 30s | WebSocket keepalive |
| TradeIngestion flush | 2s | Batch flush trades |
| PriceMonitor | 15s | Check prices for ladders/stop-loss |
| ArbScanner | 60s | Scan for arb opportunities |
| BalanceTracker | 5 min | Refresh USDC balance |
| SmartStopLoss | 30s | Check stop-loss conditions |
| Frontend refresh | 5s | Dashboard auto-refresh |

### Reconnect strategies
- ChainListener: 3s initial → 60s max (exponential backoff)
- DomeWebSocket: 3s delay, max 50 attempts

