## 15. ERROR HANDLING PATTERNS

### Retry with backoff (`polymarketApi.ts`)
- Retries on: 429, 500, 502, 503, 504, ECONNRESET, ETIMEDOUT, ENOTFOUND
- Max 3 retries, 1s base delay, exponential backoff

### Trade execution failures (`tradeExecutionDiagnostics.ts`)
- `classifyTradeExecutionFailure()` categorizes: MARKET_CLOSED, AUTH_SIGNATURE, ORDER_PAYLOAD, etc.
- One retry on invalid signature errors

### Storage fallback
- If SQLite init fails, falls back to JSON storage

### Fail-safe pattern
- Trade safety checks default to BLOCKING on error (never proceed if status unknown)

